content.warning: Kubera ko iyi porogaramu isaba umubare munini wuruhushya kuri terefone yawe igendanwa, uruhushya rwinshi rushobora guteza akaga cyane, ntitugumane cyangwa ngo mutabinjire tutamenye neza ingaruka zingufu cyangwa inyandiko. Umaze kwinjiza ibirimo muri "Ikarita yisoko Intangiriro" cyangwa "Isoko ryurubuga rwigenga" agasanduku kanditse hepfo, ibirimo bizakorwa ako kanya nkuko kode. Nyamuneka witondere.
